2. Cash Flow Waterfall Framework

Understanding how money flows through an investment.

Flow sequence

Revenue
→ Operating Expenses
→ Net Operating Income
→ Debt Service
→ Cash Flow to Equity

Why it matters

It clarifies:

• asset performance
• debt obligations
• investor returns

