Rental Operations

Investment Analysis

3. Cap Rate Valuation Framework

Core valuation relationship:

Value = NOI ÷ Cap Rate

Interpretation

Cap rate represents:

• required return
• perceived risk
• capital market conditions

Key insight

Small cap rate changes cause large valuation changes.

