4. Leverage Sensitivity Framework

Analyzing how debt affects investment outcomes.

Key variables

• Loan-to-value
• Interest rate
• Amortization
• Holding period

What investors test

How returns change when:

• interest rates rise
• rents fall
• refinancing conditions change

